<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.wws.princeton.edu/ota/ns20/alpha_f.html" class="external text" title="http://www.wws.princeton.edu/ota/ns20/alpha_f.html" rel="nofollow">"<i>Copper: Technology &amp; Competitiveness (Summary)</i> Chapter 6: Copper Production Technology"</a>. Office of Technology Assessment. 2005<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.wws.princeton.edu/ota/ns20/alpha_f.html" class="external free" title="http://www.wws.princeton.edu/ota/ns20/alpha_f.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.wws.princeton.edu/ota/ns20/alpha_f.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=%27%27Copper%3A+Technology+%26+Competitiveness+%28Summary%29%27%27+Chapter+6%3A+Copper+Production+Technology&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.pub=Office+of+Technology+Assessment&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wws.princeton.edu%2Fota%2Fns20%2Falpha_f.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Copper"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
